### Habit Tracker API Test Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5134
@userId = test-user-1

### Get all habits
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habits?userId={{userId}}

### Get active habits only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habits/active?userId={{userId}}

### Get specific habit by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habits/1?userId={{userId}}

### Get habit statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habits/1/stats?userId={{userId}}

### Create a new habit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/habits?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Meditation",
  "description": "Daily mindfulness meditation practice",
  "category": "Wellness",
  "frequency": 1,
  "targetCount": 1,
  "unit": "minutes",
  "targetValue": 15,
  "colorCode": "#9B59B6",
  "startDate": "2024-10-31"
}

### Update an existing habit
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/habits/1?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning Exercise - Updated",
  "description": "Extended morning exercise routine",
  "category": "Health",
  "frequency": 1,
  "targetCount": 1,
  "unit": "minutes",
  "targetValue": 45,
  "colorCode": "#E74C3C",
  "isActive": true
}

### Create a habit entry
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "habitId": 1,
  "completedAt": "2024-10-31T08:00:00Z",
  "count": 1,
  "actualValue": 35,
  "notes": "Great morning workout session!",
  "rating": 8,
  "location": "Home gym",
  "durationMinutes": 35
}

### Get entries for a specific habit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries/habit/1?userId={{userId}}

### Get entries for a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries/date/2024-10-31?userId={{userId}}

### Get recent entries (last 7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries/recent?days=7&userId={{userId}}

### Get specific habit entry
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries/1?userId={{userId}}

### Update a habit entry
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries/1?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completedAt": "2024-10-31T08:00:00Z",
  "count": 1,
  "actualValue": 40,
  "notes": "Updated: Excellent workout with extra cardio",
  "rating": 9,
  "location": "Home gym",
  "durationMinutes": 40
}

### Delete a habit entry
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/habitentries/1?userId={{userId}}

### Delete a habit (this will also delete all related entries)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/habits/1?userId={{userId}}